OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPerhaps the
OL,6,Fodd light shower at first this
OL,7,Fevening, these becoming confined to
OL,8,Fwestern Argyll overnight with the rest
OL,9,Fof the region dry with some clear
OL,10,Fperiods. Chilly, perhaps a frost in
OL,11,Fparts of Lanarkshire.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FPerhaps the odd light
OL,14,Fshower over the Argyll Isles.
OL,15,FOtherwise a dry and bright day with
OL,16,Fsome hazy sunny spells.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,19,Fgood deal of cloud around during this
OL,20,Fperiod with showers, but some brighter
OL,21,Fperiods. Rather breezy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
